who walked among the spirits...

627
01:01:00,418 --> 01:01:01,976
and returned.

628
01:01:04,389 --> 01:01:06,118
There's power here.

629
01:01:07,091 --> 01:01:09,753
I only pray it is enough.

630
01:01:17,436 --> 01:01:20,234
Because Kane still thinks he needs her.

631
01:01:21,040 --> 01:01:23,440
He was insane when he lived.

632
01:01:23,909 --> 01:01:27,276
And now, in death, that insanity...

633
01:01:27,980 --> 01:01:29,880
has become the beast.

634
01:01:30,416 --> 01:01:32,884
He wants Carol Anne now...

635
01:01:33,352 --> 01:01:35,115
before she grows up.

636
01:01:35,822 --> 01:01:38,382
Youth is a strong life force.

637
01:01:39,326 --> 01:01:42,261
Innocence is pure life force.

638
01:01:42,762 --> 01:01:46,425
We lose strength as we lose our innocence.

639
01:01:46,900 --> 01:01:50,734
You see, innocence is the only gift
we're given in life.

640
01:01:51,571 --> 01:01:54,335
All else must be fought for.

641
01:01:55,775 --> 01:01:58,767
In that gift is purity.

642
01:02:00,080 --> 01:02:02,173
In that purity...

643
01:02:02,650 --> 01:02:04,550
lies strength.

