667
01:03:53,365 --> 01:03:55,856
Won't you join us, Carol Anne?

668
01:04:09,180 --> 01:04:10,807
- Come here!
- No!

669
01:04:40,347 --> 01:04:43,908
Don't just stand there!
Get over here, for Christ's sake!

670
01:05:24,792 --> 01:05:27,022
I got you, baby. It's okay.

671
01:05:28,696 --> 01:05:29,822
Here you go.

672
01:05:34,436 --> 01:05:36,370
You're all right.

673
01:05:36,438 --> 01:05:38,565
- Where is she?
- Carol Anne is drowning!

674
01:05:38,640 --> 01:05:40,232
- She's drowning!
- Where?

675
01:05:43,478 --> 01:05:44,843
You're safe now.

676
01:05:45,914 --> 01:05:47,006
Where?

677
01:05:48,049 --> 01:05:51,485
- She's drowning!
- What does it matter anymore?

678
01:05:51,553 --> 01:05:53,646
