696
01:07:07,465 --> 01:07:09,695
Where's my dad? I want my dad.

697
01:07:10,201 --> 01:07:11,930
Lie here and relax.

698
01:07:12,670 --> 01:07:14,467
I'll go get your dad.

699
01:07:27,920 --> 01:07:29,080
