700
01:09:47,064 --> 01:09:48,964
And they thought I was her.

701
01:10:44,791 --> 01:10:46,088
I saw her.

702
01:10:46,159 --> 01:10:48,957
- You think you saw her.
- I saw her, damn it!

703
01:10:49,462 --> 01:10:52,488
